    <note>Zhao(1) Shigan [10945] See documentation for grandson, Shanchuo [10947], and great grandson, Ruteng [10948]. Since Ruteng's younger brother, Ruyu(3) [10950], is listed in Fujian TZ, 149.48b as a Gutian county jinshi, I am assuming that the move was to Fuzhou, Gutian. He was buried in a buddhist temple in Huaian county and died 28 years before his wife, i.e. in 1141. SS(PRC), 232.7524; Lin Zhiji, WJ, 18.13a-14b (wife, n Wang(2), who died in 1169 at age 78). Not indexed in CBD.</note>
